# Loop engineering

- Read `AGENTS.md` and `progress.md` at the start of substantial tasks.
- Use subagents by role: triage → architect → developer → verifier.
- Never mark backlog items done without verifier passing acceptance criteria.
- Persist decisions and status in `progress.md`, not only in chat.
